Package spoon.support.visitor

Class SignaturePrinter

java.lang.Object
spoon.reflect.visitor.CtScanner
spoon.support.visitor.SignaturePrinter
All Implemented Interfaces:
CtVisitor
public class SignaturePrinter extends CtScanner
Responsible for computing signatures for elements where a signature exists (CtType, CtMethod and CtPackage). Otherwise returns the empty string.
